ent\" src=\"/logo.png\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-3xl -z-10 animate-pulse\"></div></div></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-full px-8 py-3 inline-block border border-primary/20\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-primary font-semibold text-lg\">Confira os melhores momentos e as equipes que fizeram história no Querido Camp</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0)\"><div class=\"glass-card w-16 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/30\"></div><div class=\"glass-card w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-primary/20\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse\"></div></div><div class=\"glass-card w-16 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/30\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1200 120\" class=\"w-full h-20 fill-current text-primary/10\"><path d=\"M0,60 C300,120 900,0 1200,60 L1200,120 L0,120 Z\"></path></svg></div></div><section class=\"py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-gray-900\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4 mb-12 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-block bg-gold/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"text-gold font-semibold\">Hall da Fama</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gold\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Equipes Campeãs</h2><p class=\"text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Conheça as equipes que se destacaram na edição anterior do Querido Camp</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12\"><div class=\"relative  glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div 